(211, 'admission_eligibility', 'What is the admission eligibility criteria?', '📋 **PMAS-Arid Admission Eligibility Criteria:**\r\n\r\n**Undergraduate (BS Programs):**\r\n\r\n📚 **General Requirements:**\r\n✅ FSc (Pre-Medical/Pre-Engineering) with 50% minimum\r\n✅ A-Levels with 2 principal passes (C grade minimum)\r\n✅ Intermediate (I.Com/FA) for relevant programs\r\n✅ DAE (3 years) for engineering programs\r\n\r\n**Subject-Specific:**\r\n\r\n🌾 **Agriculture Programs:**\r\n- FSc Pre-Medical or\r\n- FSc Pre-Engineering or  \r\n- DAE (Agriculture)\r\n- Minimum 50% marks\r\n\r\n💻 **Computer Science/IT:**\r\n- FSc Pre-Engineering (Mathematics mandatory)\r\n- A-Levels (Math + 2 sciences)\r\n- ICS (Computer Science)\r\n- Minimum 50% marks\r\n\r\n🐄 **Veterinary Sciences:**\r\n- FSc Pre-Medical (Biology mandatory)\r\n- Minimum 60% marks\r\n- Entry test mandatory\r\n\r\n📊 **Business Programs:**\r\n- FSc/FA/ICS/I.Com\r\n- Minimum 45% marks\r\n\r\n**Graduate Programs (MS/M.Phil):**\r\n\r\n✅ Relevant Bachelor\'s degree (16 years)\r\n✅ Minimum 2.50/4.00 CGPA or 50% marks (annual system)\r\n✅ GAT General (50% score) - for some programs\r\n✅ Departmental test/interview\r\n\r\n**PhD Programs:**\r\n\r\n✅ Relevant MS/M.Phil degree (18 years)\r\n✅ Minimum 3.00/4.00 CGPA in MS/M.Phil\r\n✅ GAT Subject (60% score)\r\n✅ Research proposal\r\n✅ Interview\r\n\r\n**Special Quotas:**\r\n\r\n🏅 **Reserved Seats:**\r\n- 2% for disabled persons\r\n- 2% for minorities\r\n- 1% for orphans  \r\n- 17% for merged districts (tribal areas)\r\n\r\n🎖️ **Self-Finance:**\r\nAdditional seats on self-finance basis\r\n\r\n**Age Limit:**\r\n\r\n📅 **Undergraduate:** No specific age limit\r\n📅 **Graduate:** No specific age limit\r\n📅 **PhD:** Preferably under 40 years\r\n\r\n**Domicile Requirements:**\r\n\r\n📍 **Punjab Domicile:** 90% seats\r\n📍 **Other Provinces:** 10% seats\r\n📍 **Overseas:** Special quota\r\n\r\n**Additional Requirements:**\r\n\r\n✅ Pakistani citizen (or AJK resident)\r\n✅ Good moral character\r\n✅ Medically fit\r\n✅ No criminal record\r\n\r\n**Equivalence:**\r\n\r\n🌐 **Foreign Qualifications:**\r\nMust have equivalence from IBCC or HEC\r\n\r\n**Entry Test:**\r\n\r\n📝 **Mandatory for:**\r\n- All undergraduate programs\r\n- Some graduate programs\r\n- Veterinary Sciences\r\n- Competitive programs\r\n\r\n📊 **Test Weightage:**\r\n- Entry Test: 50%\r\n- Academic Record: 50%\r\n- (May vary by program)\r\n\r\n**Merit Calculation:**\r\n\r\n📊 **Undergraduate:**\r\n50% previous academic record + 50% entry test\r\n\r\n📊 **Graduate:**\r\nVaries by program (test/interview/research)\r\n\r\n**Hafiz-e-Quran:**\r\n\r\n⭐ **Benefits:**\r\n- Fee concession\r\n- Additional weightage in merit\r\n- Certificate required from registered Madrassah\r\n\r\n**Documents Verification:**\r\n\r\n⚠️ All documents verified before admission\r\n⚠️ False information = Admission cancellation\r\n\r\n📞 **For Queries:**\r\nContact Admissions Office\r\n🌐 www.uaar.edu.pk/admissions\r\n\r\n🎯 Ensure you meet criteria before applying!', 'Admissions', 'All', 1, 'static', '2026-02-11 15:46:41', '2026-02-11 15:46:41', NULL, 'Eligibility criteria for PMAS-Arid admissions'),
(213, 'university_departments', 'What departments are available at PMAS-Arid?', '🏛 **PMAS-Arid Agriculture University – Departments & Faculties**  \r\n\r\n**🌾 Faculty of Crop & Food Sciences:**  \r\n- Agronomy: Crop production & soil fertility  \r\n- Plant Breeding & Genetics: Improved crop varieties  \r\n- Plant Pathology: Plant disease management  \r\n- Entomology: Pest management & insect studies  \r\n- Horticulture: Fruits, vegetables, ornamental plants  \r\n- Agricultural Extension & Communication: Farmer education & outreach  \r\n- Forestry & Range Management: Forest & rangeland management  \r\n\r\n**🔬 Faculty of Sciences:**  \r\n- Botany: Plant biology & ecology  \r\n- Zoology, Wildlife & Fisheries: Animal biology & conservation  \r\n- Biology: Fundamentals of living organisms  \r\n- Chemistry: Organic, inorganic, analytical chemistry  \r\n- Physics: Physical principles & applications  \r\n- Mathematics: Pure & applied mathematics  \r\n- Statistics: Research & data analysis  \r\n- Eastern Medicine: Traditional & clinical systems  \r\n\r\n**🐄 Faculty of Veterinary & Animal Sciences:**  \r\n- Veterinary Biomedical Sciences  \r\n- Veterinary Parasitology & Microbiology  \r\n- Clinical Studies  \r\n- Veterinary Pathology  \r\n\r\n**⚙️ Faculty of Agricultural Engineering & Technology:**  \r\n- Structures & Environmental Engineering  \r\n- Farm Machinery & Precision Engineering  \r\n- Land & Water Conservation Engineering  \r\n- Energy Systems Engineering  \r\n- Center for Precision Agriculture  \r\n\r\n**📊 Faculty of Social Sciences:**  \r\n- Economics & Agricultural Economics  \r\n- Sociology & Anthropology  \r\n- Humanities  \r\n- Education  \r\n\r\n**💻 Institutes & Specialized Units:**  \r\n- Biochemistry & Biotechnology  \r\n- University Institute of IT (UIIT)  \r\n- Management Sciences  \r\n- Geo-Information & Earth Observation (IGEO)  \r\n- Food & Nutritional Sciences  \r\n- Soil & Environmental Sciences  \r\n- Animal Sciences  \r\n\r\n📍 For details, visit: https://www.uaar.edu.pk  \r\n💡 You can ask me about a specific department for more info.', 'University Info', 'All', 1, 'static', '2026-02-11 16:22:01', '2026-02-11 16:22:01', NULL, 'Comprehensive list and definitions of all departments at PMAS-Arid'),
(216, 'cs_programs', 'Computer Science programs', '💻 **Faculty of Engineering & IT (UIIT)**\r\n\r\n- BS Computer Science, Software Engineering, IT  \r\n- Duration: 4 years  \r\n- Focus: Programming, Networking, Software Development  \r\n- Admission: Via entry test and merit list  \r\n\r\nMore info: 🌐 https://www.uaar.edu.pk', 'Academic Programs', 'All', 1, 'static', '2026-02-11 17:07:39', '2026-02-11 17:07:39', NULL, 'CS & IT programs under UIIT'),
(217, 'agriculture_programs', 'Agriculture faculty programs', '🎓 **Faculty of Agriculture**\r\n\r\n- BS Agronomy, Horticulture, Plant Pathology, Entomology, Soil Science, Agricultural Economics  \r\n- Duration: 4 years  \r\n- Admission: Entry test & merit list  \r\n\r\nMore info: 🌐 https://www.uaar.edu.pk', 'Academic Programs', 'All', 1, 'static', '2026-02-11 17:07:39', '2026-02-11 17:07:39', NULL, 'Agriculture programs at PMAS-Arid'),
